def test_env(tmpdir, temp_user):
    target = tmpdir
    foo = target.mkdir('foo')
    setup = target / 'setup.py'
    if setup.isfile():
        raise ValueError(dir(target))
    with setup.open('w') as f:
        f.write(SETUP_PY)
    init = foo / '__init__.py'
    with init.open('w') as f:
        f.write(INIT_PY)
    with target.as_cwd():
        yield target
